AD%E5%9C%A8%E9%98%BF%E5%AF%8C%E6%B1%97%E6%8D%B2%E5%9C%9F%E9%87%8D%E4%BE%86-%E9%84%B0%E5%9C%8B%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%8E%A1%E5%8F%96%E5%8B%99%E5%AF%A6%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%95-120113911.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>、巴基斯坦<ref>{{cite web |title=Afghanistan: Can Pakistan 'manage' the Taliban? |url=https://www.dw.com/en/afghanistan-can-pakistan-manage-the-taliban/a-58250772 |website=DW |access-date=2021-08-15 |archive-date=2021-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210815084901/https://www.dw.com/en/afghanistan-can-pakistan-manage-the-taliban/a-58250772 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和中国<ref>{{Cite news|title=中國成為塔利班的新朋友 中俄印如何面對阿富汗「改朝換代」|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-58052388|newspaper=BBC News 中文|accessdate=2021-08-14|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2021-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210813234806/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-58052388|dead-url=no}}</ref>等国以寻求支持，無後顧之憂地快速攻佔原阿富汗政府控制的大多數國土，加速了控制阿富汗更多领土的步伐，并宣布坚持政治进程<ref>{{cite web |title=塔利班宣布控制第十个省会城市与国防部证实数十名塔利班武装人员在巴尔赫地区被杀 |url=https://chinese.aljazeera.net/news/2021/8/12/阿富汗塔利班扩大实地控制并坚持政治进程与喀布 |website=ALJAZEERA |access-date=2021-08-19 |archive-date=2021-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210815084901/https://chinese.aljazeera.net/news/2021/8/12/%E9%98%BF%E5%AF%8C%E6%B1%97%E5%A1%94%E5%88%A9%E7%8F%AD%E6%89%A9%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%9E%E5%9C%B0%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%B9%B6%E5%9D%9A%E6%8C%81%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E8%BF%9B%E7%A8%8B%E4%B8%8E%E5%96%80%E5%B8%83 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，8月15日[[攻佔喀布爾_(2021年)|塔利班进入喀布尔]]後总统[[阿什拉夫·加尼·艾哈迈德扎伊|阿什拉夫·加尼·艾哈迈德扎伊]]逃往國外，阿富汗内政部公告將成立由塔利班主导的临时政府<ref>{{cite web |title=Taliban enter Kabul outskirts, await ‘peaceful transfer’ of Afghanistan capital |url=https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/world/taliban-enter-kabul-outskirts-await-e2-80-98peaceful-transfer-e2-80-99-of-afghanistan-capital/ar-AANl9XN?ocid=uxbndlbing |publisher=FOX News |access-date=2021-08-15 |archive-date=2021-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210815100347/https://www.msn.com/en-us/news/world/taliban-enter-kabul-outskirts-await-e2-80-98peaceful-transfer-e2-80-99-of-afghanistan-capital/ar-AANl9XN?ocid=uxbndlbing |dead-url=no }}</ref>，將商討如何和平進行權力過渡，而第一副總統[[阿姆魯拉·薩利赫|阿姆魯拉·薩利赫]]則於8月17日依《阿富汗憲法》就任[[阿富汗伊斯蘭共和國|阿富汗伊斯蘭共和國]]看守總統，领导[[潘杰希尔抵抗势力|潘杰希尔抵抗势力]]繼續抵抗[[塔利班|塔利班]]政權<ref name=":5">{{Cite web |title=Afghanistan crisis: Taliban give first press conference in Kabul |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/live/world-asia-58219963 |access-date=2021-08-17 |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |language=en |editor-last=Wertheimer |editor-first=Tiffany |url-status=no |archive-date=2021-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210815163031/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/live/world-asia-58219963 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=阿富汗副總統仍堅守國內 沙雷：「我是合法看守總統」 |url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3641780 |access-date=2021-08-18 |work=自由時報 |archive-date=2021-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210820045234/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3641780 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。8月19日，[[塔利班|塔利班]]在喀布爾正式宣布重新建國，國號依然為「'''阿富汗伊斯蘭酋長國'''」，訂8月19日為國慶日<ref name=塔利班高级/>。

